    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels at MRL 2. Discretization error exceeds requirement (achieved Gradation 3 vs. required 2). The UQ campaign documented in vr-uq-sobol confirms that the 5-point test matrix adequately spans the dominant variance directions in the COU operating space. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at 4 of 5 target conditions; the single marginal point (3 L/min / 4500 RPM) is outside the primary clinical operating envelope and has been accepted with engineering justification. Six factors not assessed are appropriate at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
